#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&umbrello; helps the software development process by using the industry "
"standard Unified Modelling Language (&UML;) to enable you to create diagrams "
"for designing and documenting your systems."
msgstr ""
"&umbrello; hjælper til med udviklingsprocessen for programmel ved at bruge "
"industristandarden Unified Modelling Language (&UML;) for at gøre det muligt "
"at oprette diagrammer til at konstruere og dokumentere systemer."

